{"tid":527204,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[悲劇] 俾個肥婆搞到有咗一忽頭髮","createTime":"2018-01-12T12:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T12:27:27.000Z","uid":157304,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0807861904168482ca9ab81ea0a09552ae9da82c","tid":527204,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:04:10.000Z","msg":"屌你哋班連登仔<br />\n平時成日笑柒欣宜條死肥閪<br />\n<br />\n搞到今日剪頭髮嗰陣<br />\n一喺塊鏡見到有個肥婆入嚟<br />\n即刻諗起欣宜跳斷腳個post<br />\n同你哋班撚樣啲回覆<br />\n咩吊臂、救護員受傷圖<br />\n忍唔住笑咗出嚟<br />\n震到俾髮型師鏟撚光咗一忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點救都救唔返<br />\n<br />\n你班友同死肥婆真係害人不淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84c54bc9a9408d8f4579dd7204a051b973a91bbd","tid":527204,"uid":19867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"圖?"},{"pid":"e98c4e18cccec1b00d74ab826f8c58c76b1a68aa","tid":527204,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:04:51.000Z","msg":"冇咗一忽頭髮先啱<br />\n嬲到打錯字<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"1f7332abb58b0bfd070e1c975e0393bd4dd8d1c5","tid":527204,"uid":165875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e98c4e18cccec1b00d74ab826f8c58c76b1a68aa","tid":527204,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:04:51.000Z","msg":"冇咗一忽頭髮先啱<br />\n嬲到打錯字<br />\n屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:21:10.000Z","msg":"圖"},{"pid":"8a2fac8375db9b7dbb55de7f8011720a0440eb04","tid":527204,"uid":143699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"冇圖你話同緊欣兒69都得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}